title: Has COVID killed the office?
itunes:author: Dr Grace Lordan, Dr Carsten Sorensen, Professor Connson Locke, Hailley Griffis
description: Contributor(s): Dr Grace Lordan, Dr Carsten Sorensen, Professor Connson Locke, Hailley Griffis | Joanna Bale talks to LSE’s Connson Locke, Grace Lordan and Carsten Sorensen, as well as Hailley Griffis, a social media management company executive, who believes that offices will soon become extinct.
